title: 090 - Does Foxy Lack Integrity, Respect, & Honor?
description: On today's show, the recent string of Youball controversies in the office hit a boiling point as Foxy finds himself of being barred from the league, plus the guys dive into a loaded Pod FOD that includes some of their favorite movie quote deliveries, the guy who got hit by the falling cat having a spinal cord injury, their favorite types of suckers, some of the things they're current watching, what food take they have that typically pisses people off, and what they're eyeing on Prime Day. Don't forget to subscribe to youtube.com/thepatmcafeeshow to watch full episodes of The Pod and everything else PMI related, and keep sending your questions in @ThePodPMI on Twitter and Instagram. We appreciate you all for listening. Enjoy.
